Helen Raymond https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Helen_Raymond 0 Helen Raymond (September 3, 1878 – November 26, 1965) was a stage actress who did comedy roles on Broadway, and also appeared in Hollywood motion pictures. She was born in Philadelphia, Pennsylvania.
